QueryCallback.name: GetCasenotesForActivePeriodQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: DEFENDANT_ID = ? AND AGENCY_ID= ? AND SPRVISIONENDDATE IS NULL AND CASENOTESTATUSCD != 'I'

QueryCallback.name: GetCasenotesForPriorPeriodQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: DEFENDANT_ID = ? AND AGENCY_ID= ? AND SPRVISIONENDDATE IS NOT NULL AND CASENOTESTATUSCD != 'I'

QueryCallback.name: GetCasenotesBySuperviseeIdQuery
QueryCallback.whereClause: DEFENDANT_ID = ? ORDER BY CREATEDATE DESC FETCH FIRST 10 ROWS ONLY

QueryCallback.name: AssociationQueryEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: CASENOTE_ID = CAST(? AS INTEGER) AND SUBJECTCD_ID = ?

QueryCallback.name: AssociationQueryEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: CASENOTE_ID = CAST(? AS INTEGER) AND ASSOCIATE_ID = ?
